      • findMatches

        @GetMapping("/user/home/{email}")
public java.util.List<User> findMatches​(@PathVariable(name="email")
                                        java.lang.String email)
        Gets a list of possible matches of a given user, which are User objects, sorted by the user preferences. The first possible match being the "best one" for the user, and the last possible match on the list being the "worst one".
        Parameters:
        email - the email of the user we want to get its possible matches
        Returns:
        the possible matches (User objects) of the User provided by email
